Taken from the 3rd Solo Studio album, FalzTheBahdGuy has just released the visuals for his song  ‘Le Vrai Bahd Guy’. Starting out with what seems like a comic scene we hear Falz sing in a mix of French and English in this new video.  Also ‘Le Vrai Bahd Guy’ which translates in english to “The Truth” has Falz claiming his position once again as a BahdGuy. Read More: J.Cole Just Dropped A New Freestyle “Album of the Year” Watch and  enjoy!!! 